OL,3,C600 patients given hospital equipment
OL,4,Cto be treated in their own homes
OL,6,FAlmost 600 people have been discharged
OL,7,Fearly from hospital in North Cumbria
OL,8,Fsince the launch of 'virtual wards'.
OL,10,FThe option allows patients to be given
OL,11,Fhospital equipment at their home where
OL,12,Fthey can be monitored remotely by
OL,13,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,15,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care (NCIC)
OL,16,Flaunched the project in 2023 to reduce
OL,17,Fthe time patients with respiratory
OL,18,Fillnesses spent in hospital where they
OL,19,Fare at a higher risk of infection. It
OL,20,Fhas also helped to free up hospital
OL,21,Fbeds.
