OL,3,C600 patients given hospital equipment
OL,4,Cto be treated in their own homes
OL,6,FJeanette Hodges suffers from pulmonary
OL,7,Ffibrosis, a lung condition that makes
OL,8,Fit difficult to breathe. She is
OL,9,Fcurrently a patient in West Cumberland
OL,10,FHospital's (WCH) virtual ward and has
OL,11,Fseveral apparatus to supply her with
OL,12,Foxygen in her living room.
OL,14,FThree times a day, Jeanette sends
OL,15,Freadings of her oxygen levels and
OL,16,Fblood pressure to the virtual ward
OL,17,Fteam via a tablet.
