OL,6,FCurrently, virtual wards are operating
OL,7,Ffor patients with respiratory
OL,8,Fillnesses and those living with
OL,9,Ffrailty. Another to deal with heart
OL,10,Ffailure patients is also being set up.
OL,12,FMaria Parsonage Respiratory Consultant
OL,13,FNurse at NCIC said: "Since they were
OL,14,Flaunched over 590 patients have been
OL,15,Fsupported by the Virtual Wards and
OL,16,Fwe're delighted to be part of their
OL,17,Fcontinued success."
